{
  "stem": "10549.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And not that they wanted to give us, but we requested it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they were afraid that they might-- that we might do something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- I was no condition to do anything to anybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- I was so weak.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So all those times we always were hungry, because we didn't get much-- much food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed with the farmer for two days in that house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm going out on the third day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going out for fresh air out of the farm house to the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, I see the German tanks are coming back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And on-- on one of the German tanks was an American soldier on the front, was wounded.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they put him right on the-- on the tank in order to prevent, maybe, from the Americans tank that they should shoot-- shoot them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they kept an American soldier wounded, tied down, as a shield on their tank.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when-- my-- I-- my feet was, from that wooden shoes and walking through the woods there, my feet was full of sores.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I hardly could walk because they-- we didn't have no socks, just bare-- bare shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I saw that the German tanks are coming, and there was like maybe 50 feet, a hundred feet away, I start running.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw the American trucks running-- I mean, loading few people and driving off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of my buddy, who walked out maybe 10 minutes earlier to the street, he was running after that truck, after the American soldiers' truck.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they picked him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took him, on the truck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was running after the truck, and they just drove away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said no, I'm not gonna go back, regardless of what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If they have to shoot me, I'm not going back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I kept running in the same direction what the trucks went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now the reason why what happened, what-- I believed that we were liberated by Patton troops.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Patton had a-- his way of-- was that he was always advancing, always to the front advancing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Keep on going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he did not clean out the pockets of German resistance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a few-- the three tanks hid-- hid in the woods.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the main American force kept on going, but they did not clean out the pockets of the resistance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that was the reason why the three tanks came out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I kept running in the direction where the American trucks went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And maybe a couple of miles later, I see more American troops.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they asked me if I seen German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I couldn't speak English, but whatever I told them, I told them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I said the three tanks, German tanks were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I seen that they were aware of it, and I knew that I was safe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was behind the American lines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that's how I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To treat us as Jews, [DRINKS] we were not people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were useful, but we were not people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If a German-- any German-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] decides to shoot a Jew just for the sake of it, there was-- there was very common, regardless of where or what situation or where it was.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, during my being in the ghetto, occasionally were-- were some Gestapo people which I knew very well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was-- very-- that just reminded me of something, what I tell you happened after the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I lead to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That-- there was, on the Gestapo headquarters, was one guy who was very-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was a short fellow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was limping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had one foot short.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was in-- in charge of-- of catching resistance, because there was Polish resistance, Jewish resistance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he was one of the meanest Gestapo guy I-- we knew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was very mean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He used to shoot people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to beat up people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was very mean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And many times, we heard that he used to go into the-- into the ghetto, and when he saw a Jewish man who was built nice or good looking or strong looking, he'd shoot them on the spot.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he-- he used to say, at least now I'm shooting you because someday you might be a-- a-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a person who-- who-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who might be my enemy.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he-- he used to-- he used to shoot people right on the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
